### ========================================
### SUBCATEGORIES ENDPOINTS
### ========================================

### ----------------------------------------
### GET ALL - Obtener subcategorías de una categoría
### ----------------------------------------
GET {{baseUrl}}/subcategories?category_id={{categoryId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ----------------------------------------
### CREATE - Crear subcategoría
### ----------------------------------------
POST {{baseUrl}}/subcategories
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "category_id": "{{categoryId}}",
  "name": "Supermercado"
}

